<!--3月6日 (旧暦)-->

{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 22 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|803|ja|803rd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Seii Taishōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|ja|坂上田村麻呂|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was ordered to construct {{ill|Shiwa Castle|ja|志波城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02}} . * {{ill|Einin|ja|永仁|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5 (Julian calendar {{ill|1297|ja|1297th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|March 30|ja|3月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} issued the {{ill|Einin Tokuseirei|ja|永仁の徳政令|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|ja|甲州勝沼の戦い|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . The reorganized forces of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} at Kōshū-Katsunuma.
== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
