== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680th year|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
