== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|qq=}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|qq=}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|qq=}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|qq=}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|qq=}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|qq=}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|qq=}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139th year|qq=}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711th year|qq=}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|qq=}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|qq=}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680th year|qq=}} ).
