'''March 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft}}  the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|12=draft}}  22 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|803|ja|803rd year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|qq=|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Seii Taishōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=|12=draft}} , {{ill|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|ja|坂上田村麻呂|qq=|12=draft}}  was ordered to construct {{ill|Shiwa Castle|ja|志波城|qq=|12=draft}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Einin|ja|永仁|qq=|12=draft}}  5 (Julian calendar {{ill|1297|ja|1297th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|March 30|ja|3月30日|qq=|12=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|12=draft}}  issued the {{ill|Einin Tokuseirei|ja|永仁の徳政令|qq=|12=draft}} .
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|12=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|ja|甲州勝沼の戦い|qq=|12=draft}} . The reorganized forces of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|12=draft}} , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|qq=|12=draft}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|qq=|12=draft}}  at Kōshū-Katsunuma.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|12=draft}}  1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|12=draft}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|qq=|12=draft}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=|12=draft}}  (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|qq=|12=draft}} ).
