{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月初六|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 6일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . == Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 22 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|803|ja|803rd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Seii Taishōgun|ja|征夷大将軍|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|ja|坂上田村麻呂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} was ordered to construct {{ill|Shiwa Castle|ja|志波城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} . * {{ill|Einin|ja|永仁|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5 (Julian calendar {{ill|1297|ja|1297th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|March 30|ja|3月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} issued the {{ill|Einin Tokuseirei|ja|永仁の徳政令|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - The {{ill|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|ja|甲州勝沼の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} . The reorganized forces of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} at Kōshū-Katsunuma.
== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
