== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keian|qq=}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1648|qq=}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 28|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konoe Motohiro|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuge|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1722|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1719|qq=}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoharu|qq=}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yoita Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|qq=}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1732|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaō|qq=}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1170|qq=}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 6|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Tametomo|qq=}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bushi|qq=}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1139|qq=}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1711|qq=}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 23|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|qq=}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial family|qq=}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680th year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1680|qq=}} ).
