e/Seii Taishōgun|qq=}} , {{ill|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|ja|坂上田村麻呂|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|qq=}} was ordered to construct {{ill|Shiwa Castle|ja|志波城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiwa Castle|qq=}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} . * {{ill|Einin|ja|永仁|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Einin|qq=}} 5 (Julian calendar {{ill|1297|ja|1297年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1297|qq=}} {{ill|March 30|ja|3月30日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 30|qq=}} ) - The {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|ja|鎌倉幕府|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamakura shogunate|qq=}} issued the {{ill|Einin Tokuseirei|ja|永仁の徳政令|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Einin Tokuseirei|qq=}} . * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1868|ja|1868年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1868|qq=}} {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 29|qq=}} ) - The {{ill|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|ja|甲州勝沼の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|qq=}} . The reorganized forces of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|ja|新選組|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinsengumi|qq=}} , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōyō Chinbutai|qq=}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imperial Army (Japan)|qq=}} at Kōshū-Katsunuma.
== Births == * {{ill|Keian|ja|慶安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keian|qq=}} 1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|ja|1648年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1648|qq=}} {{ill|April 28|ja|4月28日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 28|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|ja|近衛基熙|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Konoe Motohiro|qq=}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuge|qq=}} (+ {{ill|1722|ja|1722nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1722|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|ja|1719年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1719|qq=}} {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoharu|qq=}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|ja|与板藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yoita Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|qq=}} (+{{ill|1732|ja|1732nd year|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1732|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Kaō|ja|嘉応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaō|qq=}} 2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|ja|1170年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1170|qq=}} {{ill|April 6|ja|4月6日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 6|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|ja|源為朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Tametomo|qq=}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bushi|qq=}} (* {{ill|1139|ja|1139年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1139|qq=}} ) (also said to be 1177). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōei|qq=}} 8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|ja|1711年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1711|qq=}} {{ill|April 23|ja|4月23日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 23|qq=}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|qq=}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial family|qq=}} member (* {{ill|1680|ja|1680年|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1680|qq=}} ).
