March 29]] ) - The [[:en:Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma]] . The reorganized forces of the [[:en:Shinsengumi|Shinsengumi]] , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōyō Chinbutai|qq=}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imperial Army (Japan)|qq=}} at Kōshū-Katsunuma.
== Births == * [[:en:Keian|Keian]] 1 (Gregorian calendar [[:en:1648|1648]] [[:en:April 28|April 28]] ) - [[:en:Konoe Motohiro|Konoe Motohiro]] , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuge|qq=}} (+ [[:en:1722|1722]] ). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 4 (Gregorian calendar [[:en:1719|1719]] [[:en:April 25|April 25]] ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoharu|qq=}} , 2nd daimyo of [[:en:Yoita Domain|Yoita Domain]] in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|qq=}} (+[[:en:1732|1732]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Kaō (era)|Kaō]] 2 (Julian calendar [[:en:1170|1170]] [[:en:April 6|April 6]] ) - [[:en:Minamoto no Tametomo|Minamoto no Tametomo]] , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bushi|qq=}} (* [[:en:1139|1139]] ) (also said to be 1177). * [[:en:Hōei|Hōei]] 8 (Gregorian calendar [[:en:1711|1711]] [[:en:April 23|April 23]] ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|qq=}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial family|qq=}} member (* [[:en:1680|1680]] ).
