era|Meiji era]] 1 ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1868|1868]] [[:en:March 29|March 29]] ) - The [[:en:Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma]] . The reorganized forces of the [[:en:Shinsengumi|Shinsengumi]] , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōyō Chinbutai|qq=}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imperial Army (Japan)|qq=}} at Kōshū-Katsunuma.
