'''March 6''' is the 6th day of month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}  the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|qid=Q96759840|1=tomobiki}}{{efn|ja|友引|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}} . 
== Events ==
* {{ill|Enryaku|en|Enryaku|qid=Q1373176|lt=Enryaku|1=Enryaku}}  22 ( {{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|803|en|803|qid=Q30388|lt=803|1=803}}  {{ill|April 1|en|April 1|qid=Q2510|lt=April 1|1=April 1}} ) - {{ill|Shogun|en|Shogun|qid=Q131767|lt=Seii Taishōgun|1=Shogun}} , {{ill|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|en|Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|qid=Q941979|lt=Sakanoue no Tamuramaro|1=Sakanoue no Tamuramaro}}  was ordered to construct {{ill|Shiwa Castle|en|Shiwa Castle|qid=Q11491083|lt=Shiwa Castle|1=Shiwa Castle}} {{Citation needed|date=2021-02|qq=}} .
* {{ill|Einin|en|Einin|qid=Q1327307|lt=Einin|1=Einin}}  5 (Julian calendar {{ill|1297|en|1297|qid=Q5562|lt=1297|1=1297}}  {{ill|March 30|en|March 30|qid=Q2460|lt=March 30|1=March 30}} ) - The {{ill|Kamakura shogunate|en|Kamakura shogunate|qid=Q736839|lt=Kamakura shogunate|1=Kamakura shogunate}}  issued the {{ill|Einin Tokuseirei|ja|永仁の徳政令|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Einin Tokuseirei|1=Q11549866|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11549866}} .
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|qid=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}}  1 ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1868|en|1868|qid=Q7717|lt=1868|1=1868}}  {{ill|March 29|en|March 29|qid=Q2459|lt=March 29|1=March 29}} ) - The {{ill|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|en|Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|qid=Q715567|lt=Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma|1=Battle of Kōshū-Katsunuma}} . The reorganized forces of the {{ill|Shinsengumi|en|Shinsengumi|qid=Q221031|lt=Shinsengumi|1=Shinsengumi}} , the {{ill|Kōyō Chinbutai|ja|甲陽鎮撫隊|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kōyō Chinbutai|1=Kōyō Chinbutai|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11578017}} , were defeated by the {{ill|Imperial Army (Japan)|ja|官軍|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Imperial Army (Japan)|1=kangun|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10809959}}  at Kōshū-Katsunuma.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Keian|en|Keian|qid=Q1146135|lt=Keian|1=Keian}}  1 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1648|en|1648|qid=Q6941|lt=1648|1=1648}}  {{ill|April 28|en|April 28|qid=Q2534|lt=April 28|1=April 28}} ) - {{ill|Konoe Motohiro|en|Konoe Motohiro|qid=Q922862|lt=Konoe Motohiro|1=Konoe Motohiro}} , {{ill|Kuge|ja|Kugyō|1=Kugyō|2=ja|3=公卿|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuge|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q3138036}}  (+ {{ill|1722|en|1722|qid=Q6918|lt=1722|1=1722}} ).
* {{ill|Kyōhō|en|Kyōhō|qid=Q1145048|lt=Kyōhō|1=Kyōhō}}  4 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1719|en|1719|qid=Q6902|lt=1719|1=1719}}  {{ill|April 25|en|April 25|qid=Q2531|lt=April 25|1=April 25}} ) - {{ill|Ii Naoharu|ja|井伊直陽|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naoharu|1=Ii Naoharu|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11161481}} , 2nd daimyo of {{ill|Yoita Domain|en|Yoita Domain|qid=Q898364|lt=Yoita Domain|1=Yoita Domain}}  in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|Echigo Province|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}  (+{{ill|1732|en|1732|qid=Q6966|lt=1732|1=1732}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Kaō (era)|en|Kaō (era)|qid=Q1150842|lt=Kaō|1=Kaō (era)}}  2 (Julian calendar {{ill|1170|en|1170|qid=Q19681|lt=1170|1=1170}}  {{ill|April 6|en|April 6|qid=Q2506|lt=April 6|1=April 6}} ) - {{ill|Minamoto no Tametomo|en|Minamoto no Tametomo|qid=Q1339356|lt=Minamoto no Tametomo|1=Minamoto no Tametomo}} , {{ill|Bushi|ja|武将|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bushi|1=military commander|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11545923}}  (* {{ill|1139|en|1139|qid=Q19608|lt=1139|1=1139}} ) (also said to be 1177).
* {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|qid=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}}  8 (Gregorian calendar {{ill|1711|en|1711|qid=Q6866|lt=1711|1=1711}}  {{ill|April 23|en|April 23|qid=Q2527|lt=April 23|1=April 23}} ) - {{ill|Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|ja|京極宮文仁親王|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōgoku no Miya Fumihito Shinnō|1=Kyōgoku-no-miya Ayahito-shinnō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q10883186}} , a {{ill|Japanese imperial family|ja|皇族|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese imperial family|1=Imperial Family of Japan|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11581068}}  member (* {{ill|1680|en|1680|qid=Q7642|lt=1680|1=1680}} ).

